    <title>resolve()</title>
<indexterm><primary>resolve</primary><secondary>Sabre\Event\Promise</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>Sabre\Event\Promise</primary><secondary>resolve</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>resolve ( $value)</computeroutput></para>
<para>Returns a Promise that resolves with the given value.</para>

<para>If the value is a promise, the returned promise will attach itself to that promise and eventually get the same state as the followed promise.</para>

